sequenceDiagram
    title 時序圖 6/7 — 異常場景：心跳超時與恢復
    %% 說明：心跳中斷 > 3 秒 → Edge Agent 進入 safe_mode（停止 video）、R2 Bridge 發布停車指令
    %%       Cockpit 顯示 SafetyBanner + RecoveryModal（全屏 focus trap）
    %%       Operator 確認安全後點擊「恢復控制權」→ resume_control（reliable=true）
    %%       Edge Agent 確認心跳新鮮度 < 1s → leaveSafeMode → 重啟 Go Publisher 恢復串流
    %% 關鍵：雙路獨立超時（Edge + R2），恢復需 operator 手動確認

    participant O as "操作員\nOperator"
    participant CP as "Web Cockpit\n(Next.js 3011)"
    participant LK as "LiveKit SFU\n(v1.7.2)"
    participant EA as "Edge Agent\n(TypeScript)"
    participant GP as "Go Publisher\n(GStreamer + NVENC)"
    participant R2 as "R2 Bridge\n(Python ROS2)"

    CP-xLK: 心跳中斷（網路不穩 > 3s）
    par Edge Agent 超時
        EA->>EA: startHeartbeatWatcher: age > 3000ms
        EA->>EA: enterSafeMode("heartbeat_timeout")
        EA->>GP: IPC: stop (reason: safe_mode)
        GP->>LK: 停止 Video Track
        EA->>LK: DataChannel publish (SafetyEvent: safe_mode_entered)
    and R2 Bridge 超時
        R2->>R2: Watchdog: elapsed > HEARTBEAT_TIMEOUT_S=3.0
        R2->>R2: trigger_stop() → adapter.publish_stop()
        R2->>VH: ROS2 /rvep/emergency_stop (Twist zero)
        R2->>LK: DataChannel publish (SafetyEvent: safe_mode_entered)
    end
    LK-->>CP: SafetyEvent Received
    CP->>CP: SafetyBanner (amber/red tone) + Joystick disabled
    CP->>CP: RecoveryModal (全屏, focus trap)
    CP-->>O: 警示「車輛處於安全模式」
    O->>CP: 確認周圍安全 → 點擊「我已準備好 — 恢復控制權」
    CP->>LK: DataChannel publish({type:"resume_control", acknowledgement:"operator_confirmed"}, reliable=true)
    LK-->>EA: ResumeControlCommand
    EA->>EA: 檢查 lastHeartbeatAt < 1000ms
    EA->>EA: leaveSafeMode() → 重啟 Go Publisher
    EA->>GP: IPC: start (恢復串流)
    GP->>LK: 恢復 Video Track
    EA->>LK: DataChannel publish (SafetyEvent: safe_mode_left)
    LK-->>CP: 恢復正常操作
    CP-->>O: 更新 HUD + 啟用 Joystick
